precis:
Enactment of the WITHDRAWAL FROM DISPOSAL ORDER (KLUANE FIRST NATION AND
WHITE RIVER FIRST NATION, Y.T.) - which provides for the withdrawal from
disposal of land in the Yukon in order to facilitate the settlement of
land claims made by the Kluane First Nation and White River First Nation.
